OL,6, Whenever people talk about the 1980's  
OL,7, they usually call it "the decade that  
OL,8, fashion forgot" or "the rise of        
OL,9, Thatcher". Fashion and politics aside  
OL,10, however the 1980's was an incredible   
OL,11, decade to experience especially the TV 
OL,12, shows that existed back then.          
OL,14, British terrestrial television in the  
OL,15, 1980's had what no other decade had -  
OL,16, it had the very best TV shows from     
OL,17, previous decades as well as its own    
OL,18, amazing shows. I was a kid in the      
OL,19, 1980's and I watched a lot of kids TV  
OL,20, as well as a lot of gameshows.         
