OL,8, Murdoch's eye at the time it was left  
OL,9, up to the three (soon to be followed by
OL,10, four) terrestrial channels to show the 
OL,11, best of the 1960's and 1970's - but    
OL,12, only as long as they were shot in that 
OL,13, new-fangled thing called colour.       
OL,15, This was why episodes of the Morecambe 
OL,16, and Wise Show were still favourites    
