OL,6, On the gameshow front us Brits nicked a
OL,7, few formats off our American cousins   
OL,8, such as Family Fortunes and            
OL,9, Blockbusters (both of which at one     
OL,10, point were hosted by people named Bob) 
OL,11, but we also had our own brilliant shows
OL,12, such as Treasure Hunt which introduced 
OL,13, us to the beauty of the British        
OL,14, countryside and ... well, something    
OL,15, else the cameraman was always so keen  
OL,16, to focus on!                           
OL,18, Soaps were also on the rise during the 
OL,19, 1980's. The three legendary soaps of   
OL,20, Eastenders, Coronation Street and      
OL,21, Emmerdale Farm were still going strong 
OL,22, but the Australians also wanted a part 
OL,23, in this as well.                       
