OL,6, This invariably started when the       
OL,7, various ITV regions discovered old     
OL,8, episodes of a 1970's show called The   
OL,9, Young Doctors. By the time us Brits got
OL,10, to watch the 1976 episodes it was just 
OL,11, one year away from being cancelled in  
OL,12, Oz after being on their screens for    
OL,13, almost a decade! Following this we got 
OL,14, Sons and Daughters, Neighbours and then
OL,15, Home and Away! Oh what a joy!          
OL,17, Dramas also made up a part of 1980's   
OL,18, TV. From light-hearted harbour-based   
